<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧师徒四人走在山路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空提高了警惕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一个小妖冲了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家待在这里！”八戒大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我和这个小妖打！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒挥舞钉耙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小妖跳下斜坡，跑走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒追了过去，很快就不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空听见叫声和兵器碰撞的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，没看见打斗的场面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，那个小妖又爬了上来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“待在这里，悟净！”悟空大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“保护好师父！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空朝小妖冲过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咣当！他们的兵器撞在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用尽全力打。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小妖又一次跑走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空追了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和小妖消失在山坡下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空能打赢那个小妖吗？”唐僧紧张地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了。”悟净说，“可是，不知道八戒怎么样了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>希望他没事。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，那个小妖又回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净吓了一跳。“你是怎么甩掉悟空的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没等小妖回答，悟净就拿起宝仗朝小妖打去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们打在一起，尘土飞扬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净打了一下小妖的腿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小妖滚下了斜坡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净跑着追了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧站在路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>周围安静了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他听见身后传来脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧转过身，大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个巨大的胖妖怪正对着他坏笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空回到路上时，发现八戒一个人在那儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒看起来心情很不好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父和悟净哪儿去了？”悟空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒挠了挠头。“不知道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我打败小妖回到这里，所有人都不见了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你没打败小妖。”悟空说，“那小妖甩掉了你，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>回到了这里，是我跟他打的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”八戒喊道，“你疯了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>刚才我还和那小妖打呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空哼了一声。“你觉得我会相信这话吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是我刚才和那小妖打的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净气得回到路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个小妖是怎么甩掉你们俩的？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不怎么厉害啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空糊涂了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小妖没有甩掉我。刚才我还跟他打呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不可能。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你跑下山坡追他……他回来……师父在哪儿呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空握紧了拳头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们怎么能这么笨呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小妖不光只有一个，是三个！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把我们一个个引开了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，另一个妖怪——可能是那个胖妖怪，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>趁我们不在，抓走了师父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒气呼呼地说：“你说得对！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个妖怪的洞肯定就在附近。”悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们找洞吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三个人开始找妖怪的洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们很快就找到一个洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洞门关着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这会是妖怪的洞吗？”悟净问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“会知道的。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿起钉耙砸坏了门，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后对着洞里面大喊：“把唐僧放了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洞里一个小妖吓得跑进了厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>胖妖怪在用臼和杵磨调料。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那头猪来了！”小妖大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>胖妖怪继续磨调料。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没事儿！我只怕孙悟空。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也来了！”悟空朝洞里喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>胖妖怪丢下了臼和杵。“呃哦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313099</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他干咳了几声，喊道：“太晚了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们已经把唐僧吃了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>